      <title>土耳其的通货紧缩目标意味着储备积累可能需要等待</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/turkey-central-bank-chief-sees-managing-expectations-a-challenge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其面临着确保通货紧缩和重建国际储备之间的权衡，央行行长表示，这种困境可能会减少美元购买，转而控制消费者价格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/turkey-central-bank-chief-sees-managing-expectations-a-challenge</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 19:37:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
